   "body" : "Instead of writing each item to the wallet database individually, do them in batches so that the import runs faster.\r\n\r\nThis was tested by importing a ranged descriptor for 10,000 keys.\r\n\r\nCurrent master\r\n\r\n```\r\n$ time src/bitcoin-cli -regtest -rpcwallet=importbig2 importmulti '[{\"desc\": \"pkh([73111820/44h/1h/0h]tpubDDoT2SgEjaU5rerQpfcRDWPAcwyZ5g7xxHgVAfPwidgPDKVjm89d6jJ8AQotp35Np3m6VaysfUY1C2g68wFqUmraGbzhSsMF9YBuTGxpBaW/1/*)#v65yjgmc\", \"range\": [0, 10000], \"timestamp\": \"now\", \"internal\": true, \"keypool\": false, \"watchonly\": true}]'\r\n...\r\n\r\nreal\t6m56.397s\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis PR:\r\n\r\n```\r\n$ time src/bitcoin-cli -regtest -rpcwallet=importbig4 importmulti '[{\"desc\": \"pkh([73111820/44h/1h/0h]tpubDDoT2SgEjaU5rerQpfcRDWPAcwyZ5g7xxHgVAfPwidgPDKVjm89d6jJ8AQotp35Np3m6VaysfUY1C2g68wFqUmraGbzhSsMF9YBuTGxpBaW/1/*)#v65yjgmc\", \"range\": [0, 10000], \"timestamp\": \"now\", \"internal\": true, \"keypool\": false, \"watchonly\": true}]'\r\n...\r\n\r\nreal\t1m32.581s\r\n```\r\n\r\nFixes #15739",
